lementalist to be a theurgist and I went to train my saved skill pts.  Besides having the ice and earth paths that all elementalists have, i only had a new wind path as well.  I decided to train wind, but if i put pts into earth and ice, would i get the earth and ice pets?<br>
<br>
Also for my sorcerer, I trained in mind magic at lvl 5 (with body and matter magic avalaible to all mages left alone).  Now i have disorientation, telekenisis, domination and mind twisting.  Do ALL these catagories come with mind magic.....or can i specialize in these specific catagories.  Atm, i only have 3 skill branches, i thought there were more?  thanks for the help!! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uqlmph.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qlmph</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#E9D756>(12/26/01 6:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magic...</span><hr size=1> Each line of specialization has a different set of spells, for my cleric I also have three lines of spells:<br>
rejuvination-healing &amp; special ressurect spells<br>
enhancements-buffing and a regrowth-type spell line<br>
smite(my personal favorite)-stuns, nuking(holy wrath spec), mesmerization, AEdd, and a pbae shout.<br>
<br>
If you train into one line of spells fully, you are obviously more strong in that line and you will always get the highest lvl spells of that line.<br>
<br>
Now, more onto the casters side.<br>
There are a line of spells that you get at your level, not your skill level, but your experiance level. Then, your other line of spells (refrigeration, etc etc) which, to my findings, are your specialization line of spells. These are the spells which you have gotten through training in Cold, Earth, or Wind.<br>
<br>
